~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~pattern matching operator:

->like
    syntax:
        select *from <tablename> where name like "%a%";

        e.g.
        select*from student where name like "%a%";
        {ye jis bhi name mai (a) ata hoga vo sabhi dikhaye ga}

->select*from student where name like "%u%";
+----+---------+-----------+-------+---------------------+---------+
| id | name    | city      | score | created_at          | subject |
+----+---------+-----------+-------+---------------------+---------+
|  1 | mustved | Ahmedabad | 78.65 | 2026-03-09 17:00:01 | python  |
+----+---------+-----------+-------+---------------------+---------+

         select*from student where name like "a%";
        {ye jis bhi name ke suru mai (a) ata hoga vo sabhi dikhaye ga}


        select*from student where name like "%a";
        {ye jis bhi name ke last mai (a) ata hoga vo sabhi dikhaye ga}


        select*from student where name like "_a%";
         {ye jis bhi name mai ageka 1 word chode ke (a) ata hoga vo sbhi dikhaye ga}
         {ese hi jitan ham (___) isko lgaye ge utne catector chod ke ayega or ye age piche lag sakta hai (%a___)}

